OFFICES, WAREHOUSES AND RETAIL STORES UNDER LEASES EXPIRING FROM ONE TO TWENTY-EIGHT YEARS AFTER MAY 31, 2003. RENT EXPENSE WAS $183.2 MILLION, $159.9 MILLION AND $152.0 MILLION FOR THE YEARS ENDED MAY 31, 2003, 2002 AND 2001, RESPECTIVELY.

AMOUNTS OF MINIMUM FUTURE ANNUAL RENTAL COMMITMENTS UNDER NON-CANCELABLE OPERATING LEASES IN EACH OF THE FIVE YEARS ENDING MAY 31, 2004 THROUGH 2008 ARE $188.9 MILLION, $149.6 MILLION, $129.5 MILLION, $111.1 MILLION, $92.2 MILLION, RESPECTIVELY, AND

