REVENUES AND

LONG-LIVED ASSETS BY GEOGRAPHIC AREA.

GEOGRAPHICAL AREA INFORMATION IS SIMILAR TO THAT SHOWN PREVIOUSLY UNDER OPERATING SEGMENTS WITH THE EXCEPTION OF THE OTHER ACTIVITY, WHICH HAS BEEN ALLOCATED TO THE GEOGRAPHICAL AREAS

